g-dragon-police-questioning-alleged-drug-have-not-committed-drug-related-crimes-3532628">G-Dragon因涉嫌吸毒接受警方讯问：“我没有犯下毒品相关犯罪”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
